The Use of Online CB-ART Interventions in the Context of COVID-19: Enhancing
Salutogenic Coping.

Segal-Engelchin D(1), Huss E(1), Sarid O(1).

Author information: 
(1)Spitzer Department of Social Work, Ben- Gurion University of the Negev, P.O.
