Development of a salutogenic intervention for healthy eating among Dutch type 2
diabetes mellitus patients.

Polhuis KCMM(1), Vaandrager L(1), Soedamah-Muthu SS(2)(3), Koelen MA(1).

Author information: 
(1)Department of Social Sciences, chair group Health and Society, Wageningen
University and Research, Hollandseweg 1, 6706 KN, Wageningen, The Netherlands.
