Is it possible to gain energy at work? A questionnaire study in primary health
care.

Ejlertsson L(1), Heijbel B(1), Brorsson A(1), Andersson HI(2).

Author information: 
(1)Faculty of Medicine, Department of Clinical Sciences in Malmö, Lund
University, Malmö, Sweden.
