"It was Like Magic": Relationships Supporting Compassion, Creativity, and Sense
of Coherence in Nutrition Students.

Fraser K MScAHN(1), Brady J PhD(1), Lordly D EdD(1).

Author information: 
(1)Department of Applied Human Nutrition, Mount Saint Vincent University,
