Relationships and trust: Two key pillars of a well-functioning freestanding
midwifery unit.

Rocca-Ihenacho L(1), Yuill C(1), McCourt C(1).

Author information: 
(1)School of Health Sciences, Centre for Maternal and Child Health Research,
