Global health and rehabilitation education in Canada: a qualitative analysis of
experiences and perspectives of educators.

Alias A(1), Rideout M(1), You R(1), Lencucha R(1).

Author information: 
(1)School of Physical and Occupational Therapy, Faculty of Medicine, McGill
