Resilience in Health and Illness.

Babić R(1), Babić M, Rastović P, Ćurlin M, Šimić J, Mandić K, Pavlović K.

Author information: 
(1)Faculty of Health Studies, University of Mostar, 88000 Mostar, Bosnia and
