'A synergy model of health': an integration of salutogenesis and the health
assets model.

Pérez-Wilson P(1)(2), Marcos-Marcos J(3), Morgan A(4), Eriksson M(5), Lindström
B(6), Álvarez-Dardet C(2)(7).

