(2)Public Health Research Group, University of Alicante, Alicante, Spain.
(3)Department of Health Psychology, University of Alicante, Alicante, Spain.
(4)Yunus Centre for Social Business and Health, Glasgow Caledonian University in 
London, UK.
(5)Department of Health Sciences, University West, Trollhättan, Sweden.
(6)Nordic School of Public Health, NHV, Västra Frölunda, Sweden.
