Rethinking sense of coherence: Perceptions of comprehensibility, manageability,
and meaningfulness in a group of Palestinian health care providers operating in
the West Bank and Israel.

Veronese G(1), Dhaouadi Y(2), Afana A(3).

Author information: 
(1)University of Milano-Bicocca, Stellenbosch University.
(2)University of Milano-Bicocca.
