"I was worried about not being good enough". Experiences and perspectives on
pregnancy, childbirth and parenthood when living with a neuromuscular disorder - 
an exploration of everyday life challenges.

Handberg C(1)(2), Myrup P(1), Højberg AL(1).

Author information: 
(1)National Rehabilitation Center for Neuromuscular Diseases, Aarhus, Denmark.
(2)Department of Public Health, Faculty of Health, Aarhus University, Aarhus,
