Implementing Mental Health Promotion Initiatives-Process Evaluation of the ABCs
of Mental Health in Denmark.

Hinrichsen C(1), Koushede VJ(2), Madsen KR(1), Nielsen L(1), Ahlmark NG(1),
Santini ZI(1), Meilstrup C(1).

Author information: 
(1)The Danish National Institute of Public Health, University of Southern
