for Group Therapy and Group Dynamics (ÖAGG), Vienna, Austria.
(4)Specialist Faculty of Group Psychoanalysis (GPA), Austrian Working Group for
Group Therapy and Group Dynamics (ÖAGG), Vienna, Austria.
(5)Specialist Faculty of Psychodrama (PD), Austrian Working Group for Group
Therapy and Group Dynamics (ÖAGG), Vienna, Austria.
