Baruch J(1), Springs S(2), Poterack A(3), Blythe SG(4).

Author information: 
(1)Associate professor of emergency medicine, Warren Alpert Medical School at
Brown University in Providence, Rhode Island.
(2)Research associate at the Center for Evidence Synthesis in Health at the Brown
University School of Public Health in Providence, Rhode Island.
(3)Associate educator of academic and public programs at the Rhode Island School 
