suicidality, bullying, and sense of coherence of 18-year-old males: a Finnish
population-based time-trend study.

Kronström K(1)(2), Multimäki P(1), Ristkari T(2), Parkkola K(3), Sillanmäki L(2),
Sourander A(4)(5).

